Wikipedia Lookup Pidgin Plugin

Building and Installation
-------------------------
To build the plug-in run:
	$ make
	
To install the plug-in in YOUR pidgin default directory run:
	$ make install
	
After you have installed the plugin, open Pidgin and choose 
it from the Plugins Dialog.



How to use
----------
Open a conversation window and type in a word. Now select the
word, open the context-menu (right-click) and choose menu entry
Wikipedia.
More functions coming soon. 



